content.body: Hi all, it seems the best cross-over time we have for the new meeting is actually looking like Thursday, an hour before the current meeting time. In your timezone here - https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/fixedtime.html?msg=TC39+Module+Harmony+Proposed+New+Meeting+Time&iso=20231109T1600.

I'd like to propse we update the meeting time to this slot as of this coming week, and will aim to get the invite updated tomorrow to this effect, unless anyone has any scheduling constraints or queries further.
